title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Daily Derby' game
title_page: Winning numbers drawn in 'Daily Derby' game
maintext:
SACRAMENTO (AP) _ The winning numbers in Monday evening’s drawing of the California Lottery’s “Daily Derby” game were:
1st:10 Solid Gold-2nd:12 Lucky Charms-3rd:3 Hot Shot, Race Time: 1:46.17
(1st: 10 Solid Gold, 2nd: 12 Lucky Charms, 3rd: 3 Hot Shot; Race Time: one: 46.17)
Estimated jackpot: $226,000
¶ To win the grand prize, ticket-holders must match in exact order the winning race time and the first, second and third place horses. Lesser prizes are given to ticket-holders who correctly match other horses or race times.
